overview: Ring of Honor returns to the Hammerstein Ballroom in New York City, New York, USA for its 7th installment of the Manhattan Mayhem iPPV.  The card:  Three Way Tag Team Match  Coast 2 Coast (Leon St. Giovanni & Shaheem Ali) vs. The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) vs. The Dawgs (Rhett Titus & Will Ferrara)  Tag Team Match  Deonna Purrazzo & Tenille Dashwood vs. Jenny Rose & Sumie Sakai  Singles Match  El Soberano Jr. vs. Punishment Martinez  All In Qualifying Match  Cody (w/Brandi Rhodes) vs. Flip Gordon  Six Man Tag Team Match  Brian Milonas, Silas Young & The Beer City Bruiser vs. Cheeseburger, Chuckie T & Kenny King  Tag Team Match  Dalton Castle & Volador Jr. (w/Brandon & Brent) vs. Jay Lethal & Ultimo Guerrero  Ultimate Mayhem Eight Man Tag Team Match  BULLET CLUB (Hangman Page, Marty Scurll, Matt Jackson & Nick Jackson) vs. Shane Taylor & The Kingdom (Matt Taven, TK O'Ryan & Vinny Marseglia)
title: ROH: Manhattan Mayhem VII
